FBIS4-62544 "drsov095_v_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-095 Daily Report 13 May 1994 Lithuania Preliminary Investment Agreement Initialed With Italy Preliminary Investment Agreement Initialed With Italy WS1605125594 Vilnius ELTA in English 1835 GMT 13 May 94 WS1605125594 Vilnius ELTA English BFN [From "News Bulletin" No. 499] [Text] Vilnius, 13 May, ELTA -- An Italian-Lithuanian agreement on the promotion and protection of investments was initialed in Rome on Thursday [12 May], Italian Embassy reported ELTA. Italian side was represented by the Deputy Director of Foreign Ministry Mr. Cavarai and Lithuanian -- by Ambassador Stasys Lozoraitis. The agreement which will be signed in the nearest time, is yet to be completed. The agreement gives to Italian investors in Lithuania a legal framework, which will constitute an impetus to the Italian presence in Lithuania.
